{"tid":1743835,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]從輻射事件看二噁英禍害","createTime":"2019-11-21T11:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:18:23.000Z","uid":264891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"100e7313238ae4598fd72b972ed372106940a0ed","tid":1743835,"uid":264891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>P牌出Po、 喜歡的請share。 之後再深入講知名二噁英事件</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家如果有讀開歷史就會知道<br />\n以前的人們不知道輻射禍害<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會把輻射物質塗在珠寶 鐘錶</span> (Radium 顔料會出螢光)<br />\n聽起來很瘋狂對吧?? 放射性物質塗在自己嘅日用品身上?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就是當時知識不足 大家也這樣做, 就覺得沒有問題.<br />\n要説到輻射禍害 最出名的事件就是鐳女郎 (The Radium Girls)<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jEaZnOn-_ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjEaZnOn-_ms&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=e5a35073\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jEaZnOn-_ms</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n鐳女郎就是一些在輻射物質加工場上班的女士們 由於沒有任何保護裝備<br />\n一些輻射中毒的症狀會逐漸浮現<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">最誇張的是、 一些鐳女郎死後是會發螢光綠的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下來 就是二三十年多的長期訴訟<br />\n當中當然充滿著明爭暗鬥. 政府和企業當然不希望賠償和承認錯誤, 利用金錢權力打壓異見人士<br />\n終於政府 和企業敗訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n說到二噁英嘅禍害不得不提到兩個事件 (可自己google 一下，大家有興趣我再深入探討)<br />\n1) Seveso Diaster<br />\n2) Agent Orange<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6oQvC8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6oQvC8P.png&h=56bf1fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqQfPfA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqQfPfA.png&h=c9cb5c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75W3dHk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75W3dHk.png&h=35c22be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8kzknr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8kzknr.png&h=7795a602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kigR62v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkigR62v.png&h=11adbbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人讀化學出身 二噁英嘅禍害也很清楚<br />\n基本上進入人體後就很難排出<br />\n狗們 現在不會感覺到什麼特別<br />\n就和當初的鐳女郎一樣<br />\n這些 二噁英的禍害會在他的孩子<br />\n他的孩子的孩子身上發生<br />\n這些狗將來會很害怕,很後悔, 要求索償 <br />\n<br />\n「為什麼當初不說明鬼國催淚彈的禍害？」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>理所當然，就會受到政府嘅瘋狂打壓。</strong><br />\n</span>當初的打壓者就變成他日被打壓的人。<br />\n或許可以親身品嚐被催淚彈和橡膠子彈打的滋味<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得天與地嗎<br />\n人作的孽 並不是第二天就會報應<br />\n而是很長很長的時間之後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正義會遲來, 但是從來不會缺席</span></span><br />\n大家放長雙眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022ef9306a9f5476f884b314c9706434db05f055","tid":1743835,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fb9736192f0b0b768f1e0a74e21c25e9042f57","tid":1743835,"uid":259216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"beba556b959619faee1e25f0ef4f7717c3cca0e5","tid":1743835,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df04fa4d74151980abf3edaacdd45845679a87d","tid":1743835,"uid":264891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\